OCTASPIRE/OX-OCTASPIRE-CSS

Home » ox-octaspire-css

A CSS for Emacs Org mode HTML exports. It should be usable with any Org HTML export, but it is designed specially for ox-base64-html exported HTML5 files.

The CSS file is generated with Common Lisp LASS and contains two IBM Plex fonts embedded in it.

  • style.css
  • base64-style.org
  • file-style.org
